com.yworks.yfiles.graph

Class ConsumerUndoUnit<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.AbstractUndoUnit
      • com.yworks.yfiles.graph.ConsumerUndoUnit<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the single parameter that is passed to the delegate.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUndoUnit, IDisposable, AutoCloseable

    public final class ConsumerUndoUnit<T>
extends AbstractUndoUnit
    A convenience implementation of the IUndoUnit interface that uses simple delegates for the actual undo and redo operations.
